org.apache.hadoop.yarn.server.resourcemanager.placement

Class ApplicationPlacementContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.yarn.server.resourcemanager.placement.ApplicationPlacementContext

  • public class ApplicationPlacementContext
extends Object
    Each placement rule when it successfully places an application onto a queue returns a PlacementRuleContext which encapsulates the queue the application was mapped to and any parent queue for the queue (if configured)
